Incredible! I grilled this, forming the finger-shaped meatballs around flat skewers, and that worked out great. I used sweet Pimenton de la Vera paprika, and found that to my taste it was right on the edge of being too much paprika - the paprika was a little dominant. Suggest backing off ever so slightly on the paprika, and be aware that this is a spicy recipe, so you'd need to modify significantly to serve to young children or others who don't tolerate spice. Lovely, lovely recipe, will absolutely make this again. Served with the Lemon Herb Tabbouleh recipe from this site.

